title: Eleven: Eleven
description: Loralie Watson is a young witch, who gets kicked out of her house when she tells her boyfriend about her familys secret life style, after moving in with her fully human relatives, she meets Samson Grey..A vampire. Neither suspects the other isn't human, but both try to fight the desire they feel for one another, until a series of mysterious events happen pushing them closer together; always at 11:11.
author: Ashley Ford
